@startuml Sequence_PlataAbonament
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM #3 — Procesarea Plății unui Abonament
' REQ-7, REQ-8, REQ-16
' ============================================================
title **Diagrama de Secvență #3 — Procesare Plată Abonament**

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #636E72
  ActorBorderColor #2D3436
  LifeLineBorderColor #636E72
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  ParticipantBorderColor #2D3436
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #74B9FF
  BoxBorderColor #2D3436
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFEAA7
  BorderColor #2D3436
}

actor "Membru" as User #74B9FF
participant "Frontend\n(React SPA)" as FE #DFE6E9
participant "SubscriptionController\n(/api/subscriptions)" as SC #A29BFE
participant "PaymentController\n(/api/payments)" as PC #A29BFE
participant "SubscriptionService" as SS #00CEC9
participant "PaymentService" as PS #00CEC9
participant "SubscriptionRepository" as SR #FDCB6E
participant "PaymentRepository" as PR #FDCB6E
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #E17055
participant "Payment Gateway\n(Stripe/PayU)" as GW #E17055
participant "Serviciu Email\n(SMTP)" as EM #FDCB6E

== Faza 1: Selectare și Calcul Preț Abonament ==

User -> FE : Accesează /subscriptions/new
activate FE

FE -> SC : **GET /api/subscriptions/types**\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
activate SC

SC -> SS : getAvailableTypes()
activate SS
SS -> DB : SELECT * FROM subscription_types\nWHERE is_active = true
activate DB
DB --> SS : Lista tipuri abonament
deactivate DB
SS --> SC : List<SubscriptionTypeDTO>
deactivate SS

SC --> FE : **200 OK**\n[ { id: 1, name: "Standard",\nbase_fee: 150 },\n{ id: 2, name: "Personalizat",\nbase_fee: 200 } ]
deactivate SC

FE --> User : Afișează opțiuni abonament\n(carduri cu tip + preț bază)
deactivate FE

User -> FE : Selectează „Personalizat"\nIntroduce: 4 ședințe PT
activate FE

FE -> SC : **POST /api/subscriptions/calculate**\n{ type_id: 2, pt_sessions: 4 }
activate SC

SC -> SS : calculatePrice(typeId, ptSessions)
activate SS

SS -> SS : amount = base_fee + (pt_sessions × 50)\namount = 200 + (4 × 50) = **400 RON**

note right of SS
  **Formula REQ-8:**
  Sumă = Taxă bază + (Nr. ședințe PT × 50 RON)
  = 200 + (4 × 50) = 400 RON
end note

SS --> SC : PriceCalculationDTO\n{ base_fee: 200,\npt_sessions: 4,\npt_cost: 200,\ntotal: 400,\ncurrency: "RON" }
deactivate SS

SC --> FE : **200 OK**\n{ base_fee, pt_cost, total }
deactivate SC

FE --> User : Afișează sumar:\n┌─────────────────────┐\n│ Taxă bază:  200 RON │\n│ 4 × PT:     200 RON │\n│ ────────────────── │\n│ **TOTAL:    400 RON** │\n└─────────────────────┘\n[Plătește Online]
deactivate FE

== Faza 2: Inițiere Plată ==

User -> FE : Apasă **„Plătește Online"**
activate FE

FE -> PC : **POST /api/payments/initiate**\n{ subscription_type_id: 2,\npt_sessions: 4 }\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
activate PC

PC -> PS : initiatePayment(memberId, typeId, ptSessions)
activate PS

' ── Creează abonamentul cu status pending ──
PS -> SR : createPendingSubscription(...)
activate SR
SR -> DB : INSERT INTO subscriptions\n(member_id, type, base_fee,\npt_sessions, total_amount,\nstart_date, end_date, status)\nVALUES (?, 'personalized', 200,\n4, 400, CURRENT_DATE,\nCURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '30 days',\n'pending_payment')\nRETURNING id
activate DB
DB --> SR : { id: 501 }
deactivate DB
SR --> PS : subscriptionId = 501
deactivate SR

' ── Creează sesiune de plată la gateway ──
PS -> GW : **POST /v1/checkout/sessions**\n{ amount: 40000,  // cents\ncurrency: "ron",\nsuccess_url: ".../success?sid=501",\ncancel_url: ".../cancel?sid=501",\nmetadata: { subscription_id: 501 },\nwebhook_url: ".../api/payments/webhook" }
activate GW

GW --> PS : { session_id: "cs_live_abc123",\npayment_url: "https://checkout.\nstripe.com/pay/cs_live_abc123" }
deactivate GW

PS -> PR : savePaymentIntent(...)
activate PR
PR -> DB : INSERT INTO payments\n(subscription_id, amount, currency,\ngateway_session_id, status)\nVALUES (501, 400, 'RON',\n'cs_live_abc123', 'pending')
activate DB
DB --> PR : OK
deactivate DB
PR --> PS : OK
deactivate PR

PS --> PC : PaymentInitDTO\n{ payment_url, session_id }
deactivate PS

PC --> FE : **200 OK**\n{ payment_url:\n"https://checkout.stripe.com/..." }
deactivate PC

FE --> User : Redirecționează la\npagina de plată Stripe
deactivate FE

== Faza 3: Procesare Plată (Gateway Extern) ==

User -> GW : Completează datele cardului\nApasă „Plătește 400 RON"
activate GW

GW -> GW : Procesează tranzacția\n(verificare card, 3D Secure, etc.)

alt #E6FFE6 Plata REUȘITĂ ✅

  GW --> User : Redirecționează la\nsuccess_url

  GW ->> PC : **POST /api/payments/webhook**\n(async)\n{ event: "payment_intent.succeeded",\ndata: {\n  session_id: "cs_live_abc123",\n  amount: 40000,\n  gateway_reference: "pi_xyz789"\n}}
  deactivate GW
  activate PC

  note over PC, PS
    **Webhook Processing (async)**
    Gateway-ul trimite evenimentul
    independent de redirect-ul userului.
  end note

  PC -> PS : handlePaymentSuccess(webhookData)
  activate PS

  ' ── Verificare semnătură webhook ──
  PS -> PS : Verifică semnătura webhook\n(Stripe-Signature header)

  ' ── Actualizare abonament → active ──
  PS -> SR : activateSubscription(subscriptionId)
  activate SR
  SR -> DB : UPDATE subscriptions SET\nstatus = 'active'\nWHERE id = 501
  activate DB
  DB --> SR : OK
  deactivate DB
  SR --> PS : OK
  deactivate SR

  ' ── Înregistrare plată ──
  PS -> PR : confirmPayment(sessionId, reference)
  activate PR
  PR -> DB : UPDATE payments SET\nstatus = 'completed',\ngateway_reference = 'pi_xyz789',\npaid_at = NOW()\nWHERE gateway_session_id = 'cs_live_abc123'
  activate DB
  DB --> PR : OK
  deactivate DB
  PR --> PS : OK
  deactivate PR

  ' ── Scoatere din restricted_clients (dacă e cazul) ──
  PS -> DB : DELETE FROM restricted_clients\nWHERE member_id = ?
  activate DB
  DB --> PS : affected_rows (0 sau 1)
  deactivate DB

  ' ── Actualizare status membru ──
  PS -> DB : UPDATE members SET\nsubscription_status = 'active'\nWHERE id = ?
  activate DB
  DB --> PS : OK
  deactivate DB

  ' ── Trimitere email confirmare (async) ──
  PS ->> EM : sendPaymentConfirmation(\nmemberEmail, paymentDetails)
  activate EM
  note right of EM
    **Email trimis:**
    Subiect: „Plată confirmată"
    Conținut:
    • Abonament: Personalizat
    • Sumă: 400 RON
    • Valabil: 11.05 - 10.06.2026
    • Nr. referință: pi_xyz789
  end note
  EM --> PS : OK (async)
  deactivate EM

  PS --> PC : **200 OK** (webhook acknowledged)
  deactivate PS
  deactivate PC

  |||

  User -> FE : Pagina success_url se încarcă
  activate FE
  FE -> SC : **GET /api/subscriptions/current**\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
  activate SC
  SC -> SS : getCurrentSubscription(memberId)
  activate SS
  SS -> DB : SELECT * FROM subscriptions\nWHERE member_id = ?\nAND status = 'active'
  activate DB
  DB --> SS : SubscriptionEntity (active)
  deactivate DB
  SS --> SC : SubscriptionDTO
  deactivate SS
  SC --> FE : **200 OK**\n{ type: "Personalizat",\nstatus: "active",\nstart: "11.05.2026",\nend: "10.06.2026",\ntotal: 400 }
  deactivate SC

  FE --> User : ✅ „Plata a fost procesată\ncu succes!\nAbonamentul dvs. este activ\npână la 10.06.2026."
  deactivate FE

else #FFE6E6 Plata EȘUATĂ ❌

  GW --> User : Redirecționează la\ncancel_url
  deactivate GW

  GW ->> PC : **POST /api/payments/webhook**\n(async)\n{ event: "payment_intent.failed",\ndata: {\n  session_id: "cs_live_abc123",\n  error: "card_declined"\n}}
  activate PC

  PC -> PS : handlePaymentFailure(webhookData)
  activate PS

  PS -> SR : failSubscription(subscriptionId)
  activate SR
  SR -> DB : UPDATE subscriptions SET\nstatus = 'payment_failed'\nWHERE id = 501
  activate DB
  DB --> SR : OK
  deactivate DB
  SR --> PS : OK
  deactivate SR

  PS -> PR : failPayment(sessionId)
  activate PR
  PR -> DB : UPDATE payments SET\nstatus = 'failed'\nWHERE gateway_session_id = 'cs_live_abc123'
  activate DB
  DB --> PR : OK
  deactivate DB
  PR --> PS : OK
  deactivate PR

  PS --> PC : **200 OK**
  deactivate PS
  deactivate PC

  User -> FE : Pagina cancel_url se încarcă
  activate FE
  FE --> User : ❌ „Plata nu a putut fi procesată.\nVă rugăm să reîncercați."\n[Reîncearcă Plata →]
  deactivate FE

end

@enduml
